{"tid":1412865,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[食物安全] 雞蛋","createTime":"2019-08-05T08:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:08:14.000Z","uid":157454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d23e305787ab882cf546eb6655788708fc8b77","tid":1412865,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">細菌入侵雞蛋會令雞蛋發臭</span><br />\n<br />\n以下行為會增加雞蛋發臭嘅風險<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 洗雞蛋 (破壞雞蛋表層膜)<br />\n- 將雞蛋存放於潮濕悶熱的環境 (加速細菌增長)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n留意翻 發臭嘅雞蛋係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔適合食用</span><br />\n見到路邊嘅臭蛋<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好煮嚟食</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明報 Hot Pick 摘錄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick/20170812/1500979793706/%E3%80%90%E8%9B%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%96%91%E5%95%8F%E3%80%91%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%AA%E6%AB%83-%E6%B4%97%E5%94%94%E6%B4%97%E5%A5%BD-%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%B4%97%E5%AE%8C%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E7%85%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick%2F20170812%2F1500979793706%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2595%258F%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%259B%259E%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25AB%2583-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25AE%258C%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%2588%25BB%25E7%2585%25AE&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWI093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=37d83ccb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick%2F20170812%2F1500979793706%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%259B%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2595%258F%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%259B%259E%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25AB%2583-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25AE%258C%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%2588%25BB%25E7%2585%25AE&h=fb6dc27d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick/20170812/1500979793706/%E3%80%90%E8%9B%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%96%91%E5%95%8F%E3%80%91%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%94%BE%E9%9B%AA%E6%AB%83-%E6%B4%97%E5%94%94%E6%B4%97%E5%A5%BD-%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%B4%97%E5%AE%8C%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E7%85%AE</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n1.雞蛋要清洗嗎？<br />\n在一般情況下，雞蛋是不用清洗的。蛋殼上有6000至1萬個小孔，亦有一層名為「表層膜」的保護外膜，阻止蛋殼上的細菌滲入蛋內。弄濕蛋殼可能有利微生物進入蛋內，殘留在蛋殼上的水亦可能有利細菌繼續生存。此外，清洗不當亦可能破壞蛋殼的表層膜。<br />\n<br />\n雞蛋若被禽鳥糞便污染，可以用水清洗（如有需要可用家居洗滌劑輔助），清洗後應立即烹煮。<br />\n<br />\n2.雞蛋要存放在雪櫃？<br />\n雞蛋容易腐壞，低溫儲存可減慢沙門氏菌等微生物的生長。雞蛋宜存放在一個陰涼及乾爽的地方，最好存放在雪櫃內，並與熟食及即食食物分開存放，避免與其他食物交叉污染。如雞蛋包裝上註明存放方法，應遵照包裝或標籤上的食用日期及貯存溫度存放。</span>"}]}